⚠️ To view the name of the software, you need to hover the cursor over the image ( * = special modules ). ⚠️

⚠️ Before installing an operating system, or simply before restoring a previous backup, go to the advanced partition formatting settings and select everything except the external SD card. ⚠️

⚠️ Maximum caution when working with ADB (Ex: Never delete the system launcher. Do not uninstall the dependencies and essential system modules). ⚠️

⚠️ ADB Uninstall command: adb shell pm uninstall --user 0 com.package.example ⚠️

⚠️ Operating with the ADB method, it is possible to uninstall system apps that take up resources and space or consume the battery, however one must proceed with great caution (even if it does not require root access). ⚠️
